nist-800-37 pack — content licence
===================================

This pack is derived from:
    NIST SP 800-37 Rev 2 (Risk Management Framework for Information Systems and
    Organizations: A System Life Cycle Approach for Security and Privacy)
    NIST (US Department of Commerce), Revision 2 (December 2018)

Source licence: Public Domain (US Government work, 17 U.S.C. 105)  (tier 1 — see
../../docs/SOURCE-VETTING.md)
No source-material download link is published (see ../../docs/LICENSING.md).

